1. *Mirni* ljudi često ne privlače pažnju. (Peaceful people often don't attract attention.)
2. Ovaj grad je *mirniji* od prestonice. (This city is calmer than the capital.)
3. *Mirna* luka je uvek dobrodošla nakon burne oluje. (A calm harbor is always welcome after a stormy weather.)
4. Kada ste *mirni*, lakše donosite odluke. (When you're calm, it's easier to make decisions.)
5. *Mirno* spavaj, sutra je novi dan. (Sleep peacefully, tomorrow is a new day.)
6. U *mirnom* okruženju deca se najbolje razvijaju. (Children develop best in a peaceful environment.)
7. Njegove ruke su bile *mirne* dok je držao instrument. (His hands were steady while holding the instrument.)
8. *Mirnim* glasom je pokušao da umiri uznemirenu osobu. (He tried to calm down the agitated person with a peaceful voice.)
9. Pogled na *mirne* planine smiruje dušu. (The sight of peaceful mountains soothes the soul.)
10. *Mirne* reke teku sporo i tiho. (Calm rivers flow slowly and quietly.)